summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Engineering Department, providing for the preparation of plans, specifications, estimates, acquisition of right of way for the improvement of Southwest Roxbury Street as an urban arterial between 24th Avenue Southwest and 28th Avenue Southwest (Unit A), and between 4th Avenue Southwest and 18th Avenue Southwest (Unit B), and for construction of said Unit A and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Arterial City Street Fund therefor.
